<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>śrīgaṇādhipatayē namaḥ</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> namastuṁgaśiraścuṁbicaṁdra<unclear>cāmaracāra</unclear>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> trayilōkyanagarāraṁbhamūlastaṁbhāya śaṁbhavē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="3"/>jayābhyudaya śakavaruṣa 1338 neya varttamāna ma(ṁ)nmathasaṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vatsarada jēṣṭa śu 12 sōmavāradalu svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmaṁnmahārājādhirāja
<lb n="5"/>rājaparamēśvara śrīvīrapratāpa dēvarāyamahārāyaru vijayānaga
<lb n="6" break="no"/>(ri)rya rājadhāniyaliddu sakalasāṁbrājyava nāḷuva kāladali Ā dēva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rāyamahārāyara nirūpadiṁda bārakkūrarājyavanu śaṁkara
<lb n="8" break="no"/>dēvavoḍeyaru pratipālisuva kāladalli Ānaṁdasarasvatīśrīpādaṁga
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḷa śiṣyaru Āmrutapragñaru nārāyaṇagiriga<unclear>ḷu</unclear> muguhinagrāmada
<lb n="10"/>mūṟugrāmadali baradu naṭṭa śāsanadalidda Aramanege naḍava
<lb n="11"/>ga 36 r <unclear>9</unclear> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tamage baha Akki mū 27 <unclear>ṟa</unclear>voḷage cauḷiyakērya śaṁka
<lb n="12" break="no"/>radēvaOḍeyara maṭhadali vobba brāhmaṇaṁge mū 10 Akkiyanū dhārā
<lb n="13" break="no"/>pūrvvakavāgi yeṟadukoṭṭaru mēlāda mū 17 Akkiyanū Amruta
<lb n="14" break="no"/>pragñaru <unclear>ye</unclear>ttikoṁbaru Ā mūṟugrāmada brā(ṁ)hmaṇariṁge vūnu
<lb n="15"/>satru baṁdare Arasiṁga biṁnahaṁmāḍi cauḷiyakēryya Aya
<lb n="16" break="no"/>navaru halarū pālisikoṁḍu baharu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō harēti
<lb n="17"/>vasuṁdharā[ṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] ṣaṣṭirvvaruṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimiḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
